title: The GB Sizzler
description:
The Sizzler is a chopped down thruster with a surf inspired swallowtail. The shape is wide to offer ample footspace for hard slashes on banks, powering down the line, or carving tight pocket turns and cutbacks.
L: 31.75"
W: 9.00"
WB: 17.00"
